\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\npizza 完來可以煎出黎"},{"pid":"71ccbe02b8e365b2922e01a61699021702674f99","tid":357590,"uid":4548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T05:41:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好正咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你要不要食譜</blockquote><br />\ni need~~~~~</blockquote><br />\n~~~</blockquote><br />\n個pizza 底 我係跟呢個<br />\n<a href=\"http://nw0912.pixnet.net/blog/post/41641735-%E7%B6%93%E5%85%B8%E7%91%AA%E6%A0%BC%E9%BA%97%E7%89%B9%E6%8A%AB%E8%96%A9%E9%A3%9F%E8%AD%9C%28%E5%85%A7%E5%90%AB%E7%BE%A9%E5%BC%8F%E8%96%84%E8%84%86%E9%A4%85%E7%9A%AE%E5%81%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnw0912.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F41641735-%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%2585%25B8%25E7%2591%25AA%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E9%25BA%2597%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%258A%25AB%25E8%2596%25A9%25E9%25A3%259F%25E8%25AD%259C%2528%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%2590%25AB%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E5%25BC%258F%25E8%2596%2584%25E8%2584%2586%25E9%25A4%2585%25E7%259A%25AE%25E5%2581%259A&d=qLfabYGr96qrIYdSPxS63i7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=77cfa62f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://nw0912.pixnet.net/blog/post/41641735-%E7%B6%93%E5%85%B8%E7%91%AA%E6%A0%BC%E9%BA%97%E7%89%B9%E6%8A%AB%E8%96%A9%E9%A3%9F%E8%AD%9C%28%E5%85%A7%E5%90%AB%E7%BE%A9%E5%BC%8F%E8%96%84%E8%84%86%E9%A4%85%E7%9A%AE%E5%81%9A</a><br />\n<br />\n試過幾個，呢個口感比較啱我 有咬口啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n發酵嗰陣準備埋啲配料 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">蝦 去腸( 8-10粒, 隨個人喜好加減) </span><br />\n落 鹽，黑椒，paprika , 少少香草 ，檻欖油 撈埋醃咗一個鐘 <br />\n切埋啲彩椒粒，洋蔥切細條，🌽都係切粒 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後，係焗盤搽啲油，慢慢搓塊麵團 搓到圓碌碌咁 放係焗盤上。 加一大pat 千島醬 我係iHerb 買。好健康咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同平時嗰啲差不多味，不過冇咁濃<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/13/133555_ca1787bf1980ea2d62ab0b3c4068093b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F13%2F133555_ca1787bf1980ea2d62ab0b3c4068093b.jpg&h=efc4da74&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/13/133556_bb472ee39a1d9a34cba727b4e893ea93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F13%2F133556_bb472ee39a1d9a34cba727b4e893ea93.jpg&h=c746ba7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後鋪晒啲材料，最後加芝士 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n210度焗20分鐘。 你因應返個情況，如果唔夠燶 可以焗耐多陣 等佢色水好睇啲<br />\n因為我食得比較淡味，所以調味料，醬，芝士 我都落得少啲 你地整時 應該落返多少少"},{"pid":"958c36fb92e24bb354f4baaa4d65edeac38fda84","tid":357590,"uid":4548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T05:42:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該煮一打雞翼呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n太多肉，不了"},{"pid":"73d02faf59cfbd8d9656caab029188240043bf68","tid":357590,"uid":4548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T05:42:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雞翼點整<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做完尖 繼續打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15029f3dcd35ae57cd4ec1d5999688c700290d5b","tid":357590,"uid":43523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T05:42:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洋蔥好似好生<br />\n如果落左菠蘿就正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係咪戇鳩架 pizza落菠蘿"},{"pid":"8d93f6ae2d44dd48d914ec8f0be1953763914404","tid":357590,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T05:42:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>應該煮一打雞翼呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmo